 Results are now driven in part by the 1994-2018 era in addition to the
 1948-1992 era.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Despite censored outcome variables for the modern era of 1994-2018, column
 (9) in Table 7 suggests higher place medalists earn a significantly greater
